Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.34,0:00:48.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我开动了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.74,0:00:50.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我开动了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.70,0:00:51.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我开动了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.34,0:02:30.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自从礼弥变成了僵尸以来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.33,0:02:33.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就开始拍摄礼弥的观察记录
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.83,0:02:37.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个记录不管何时  从不间断
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.93,0:02:42.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个记录不管何时  从不间断
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.47,0:02:46.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  我吃饭的时候就不用拍了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.03,0:02:50.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在说什么啊  这样的话就不是观察记录了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.88,0:02:53.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话虽然是这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.39,0:02:56.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧  所以说了  正常地吃饭就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.60,0:02:58.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  千纮
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.49,0:03:02.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你没好好吃饭才对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.99,0:03:04.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你给我适可而止吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.28,0:03:06.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.71,0:03:19.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,礼弥小姐是素食主义者啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.00,0:03:21.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…是的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.70,0:03:27.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,NO！  为…为什么味噌汤里放田螺
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.24,0:03:30.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爷爷  那是蚬贝
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.71,0:03:34.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶  诶…  是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.64,0:03:57.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根据礼弥所言  我知道了几件事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.74,0:04:01.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先  僵尸似乎不需要睡眠
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.25,0:04:04.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然可以更有意义地利用时间
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.48,0:04:06.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但因为我们都需要正常睡眠
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.52,0:04:08.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以礼弥貌似会感到很无聊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.63,0:04:18.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然会去冲澡  但却不会流汗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.52,0:04:23.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且…  应该也不会进行排泄
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.17,0:04:27.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了维持复活药的效果
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.35,0:04:30.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每隔数小时就要吃一次紫阳花的叶子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.87,0:04:42.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴布就好像是吐出积在胃里的毛一样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.42,0:04:45.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将吃下的紫阳花弄成圆球吐出
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.39,0:04:47.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概礼弥也会做相同的事…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.83,0:04:55.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果真的是那样的话  真想拍下这个瞬间啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.63,0:05:05.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐  呐  嘴里不吐些什么出来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.88,0:05:09.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在期待些什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.89,0:05:17.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那么作为允许你拍我的条件
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.46,0:05:19.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也要听我说的话
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.64,0:05:23.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是一般的女孩子做的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.66,0:05:25.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.49,0:05:30.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐  降谷君
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.59,0:05:39.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这件怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.69,0:05:42.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  嗯  这件还不错吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.09,0:05:46.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  降谷君  给我认真看看
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.89,0:05:49.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难得来挑衣服啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.29,0:05:52.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过  但是啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.41,0:05:55.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你从刚才开始就一直犹豫不决
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.28,0:05:58.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为这可是降谷君买给我的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.09,0:06:02.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我当然想要选件最好的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.69,0:06:06.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是已经过了一个小时了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.25,0:06:09.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能买个帽子吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.49,0:06:12.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以啦  不过总额要限制在一万日元以内哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.43,0:06:19.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的零用钱啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.10,0:06:25.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阴天还算好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.61,0:06:27.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么大白天的外出
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.39,0:06:31.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身体的腐坏会加快的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.05,0:06:35.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就这么想要购物啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.10,0:06:42.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拍下这种镜头也没什么意义
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.78,0:06:47.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又不是欢送会上播放的视频
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.51,0:06:52.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  所以我认为这个颜色和客人您比较配
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.72,0:07:01.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看吧  果然很配啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.11,0:07:06.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.05,0:07:12.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算这么理所当然的事  礼弥也肯定从来没得到过批准
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.35,0:07:26.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天比起平时能更加悠闲地泡个澡了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.30,0:07:35.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  真爽
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.39,0:07:41.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大白天来泡澡  果然不错
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.69,0:08:05.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然这么说…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.66,0:08:09.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…  必须得对她负起责任
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.12,0:08:17.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这澡泡得并不爽啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.08,0:08:27.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么认真的千纮
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.55,0:08:29.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是第一次见到
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.37,0:08:36.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然散华同学变成僵尸的背后肯定有不少故事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.25,0:08:42.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算如此  一声不吭就开始同居…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.08,0:08:48.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微变胖了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.45,0:08:55.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  真是的  总是礼弥礼弥的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.98,0:08:57.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对我也给点…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.88,0:09:01.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  你好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.73,0:09:03.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  小萌路
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.76,0:09:05.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真巧啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.11,0:09:07.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.38,0:09:08.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.68,0:09:12.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失礼了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.34,0:09:15.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丸子殿下你也大白天的就来澡堂
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.49,0:09:19.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…嗯  上午就帮家里干完活了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.69,0:09:21.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就来转换下心情
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.94,0:09:26.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  小萌路也和朋友一起来洗澡？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.42,0:09:29.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是说刚出门回来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.76,0:09:33.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  只是代替喝茶来洗个澡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.77,0:09:38.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说起来  千纮现在在家吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.74,0:09:44.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  哥一早就到邻镇的购物中心去了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.03,0:09:47.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说是去给礼弥殿下买衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.85,0:09:52.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两个人去快活了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.60,0:10:00.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的  那就和小萌路你们一起再洗一回澡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.84,0:10:02.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一泡解千愁
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.19,0:10:07.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三人都一直陪我到傍晚吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.89,0:10:15.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会泡晕的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.39,0:10:24.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让你久等了  降谷君
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.85,0:10:29.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很合身嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.28,0:10:31.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？  你刚才说什么了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.03,0:10:33.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么都没说啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.87,0:10:36.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶  明明说了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.34,0:10:37.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没说啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.64,0:10:41.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说了啊  你再说一遍吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.11,0:10:48.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  降谷君你也买了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.25,0:10:49.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？  对
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.62,0:10:53.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶  是什么啊  让我看看
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.21,0:10:55.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛  有什么好看的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.82,0:11:00.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  那接下来要去哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.70,0:11:02.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还要逛下去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.61,0:11:05.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  还要还要逛个够哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.92,0:11:07.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,报告
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.58,0:11:11.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目标现在位于市内的购物中心
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.68,0:11:14.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貌似就和那个降谷两个人而已
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.71,0:11:16.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有何吩咐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.79,0:11:19.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.42,0:11:22.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和之前一样继续监视
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.68,0:11:25.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  那个  我能进去看吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.12,0:11:28.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有必要着急
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.68,0:11:31.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等待时机
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.20,0:11:34.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后礼弥一个人的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.09,0:11:37.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就下手
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.18,0:11:39.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.29,0:11:51.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个制作得很好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.60,0:11:54.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是明显有些粗糙
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.16,0:11:59.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特别是这个缝纫方式  能更细致点就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.23,0:12:02.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对吧  降谷君也是这么…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.32,0:12:03.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.66,0:12:13.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,降谷君居然会怕鬼屋  真是没想到
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.18,0:12:16.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了  有什么不好的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.89,0:12:21.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜欢僵尸恐怖电影之类  但是那种就另当别论了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.95,0:12:24.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶  是这样的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.69,0:12:28.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说起来你啊  怎么说呢胆子还挺大…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.91,0:12:34.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了  瞧不起我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.78,0:12:39.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算这样还是为了我一起进去了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.13,0:12:43.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你  降谷君
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.75,0:12:54.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了  反正没有下次了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.05,0:12:55.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.48,0:12:59.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有啊  这个
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.66,0:13:03.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之后天气还会变得更热
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.35,0:13:06.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这里面放点干冰穿着的话
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.60,0:13:08.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该能够缓解身体的疼痛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.64,0:13:11.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样外出应该也不会有什么问题了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.66,0:13:15.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有  你看啊  比如上学等等
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.94,0:13:17.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  该怎么说呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.06,0:13:22.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,普通的女孩子能做的事  应该都能做得到了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.51,0:13:24.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,降谷君
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.86,0:13:25.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.35,0:13:30.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.39,0:13:34.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了  这个有什么不好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.13,0:13:37.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是  不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.33,0:13:43.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,降谷君  真的在为我着想
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.93,0:13:45.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我高兴得…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.69,0:13:48.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.13,0:13:52.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一次知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.13,0:13:57.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,僵尸就算哭也流不出眼泪来呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.85,0:14:00.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.14,0:14:00.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.08,0:14:04.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.11,0:14:09.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为本来以为你通晓僵尸的一切
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.93,0:14:14.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以就好奇居然还有降谷君不知道的事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.08,0:14:17.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个当然有了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.61,0:14:22.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会全部告诉你的哦  僵尸的知识
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.58,0:14:28.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,礼弥  虽然你以为自己自由了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.51,0:14:29.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但那是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.55,0:14:35.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虚假的自由
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.81,0:14:41.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确实你或许会觉得我的教导有些严格
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.35,0:14:46.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是要是以为逃走便是自由的话
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.12,0:14:48.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就错了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.72,0:14:53.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  回来吧  礼弥
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.31,0:14:57.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来告诉你什么是真正的自由吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.03,0:15:14.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  不好  差不多要吃饭了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.75,0:15:18.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也去买点吃的东西了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.37,0:15:20.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很快就回来  你先吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.58,0:15:21.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.82,0:15:37.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃的东西就有点单调了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.16,0:15:41.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毕竟不能和降谷吃一样的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.99,0:15:48.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过这也是没办法的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.97,0:15:52.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为是僵尸  肠子都坏掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.61,0:15:57.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,散华
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.06,0:16:01.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,礼弥同学
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.09,0:16:06.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.87,0:16:15.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊呀  真巧啊  竟然能在这里相遇
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.50,0:16:20.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼  是命运吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.54,0:16:23.08,Note2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙是啥{\i1}! {\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.57,0:16:27.08,Note2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道  但是不管怎样先等等看{\i1}! {\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.58,0:16:28.62,Note2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了  了解
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.97,0:16:31.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.39,0:16:37.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在说什么啊  之前一起度过美妙一刻的康孝啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.40,0:16:39.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,降谷的好朋友啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.07,0:16:41.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  操场上的那位
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.95,0:16:43.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来要去买东西吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.62,0:16:45.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  已经买过了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.62,0:16:48.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs20}原来如此  正是悠闲时间啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.14,0:16:48.85,Note2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办  要报告给团一郎大人吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.28,0:16:50.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs20}那么有个很好的去处哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.31,0:16:51.60,Note2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  再稍微等等看
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.92,0:16:53.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs20}来来  打铁趁热赶快去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.98,0:16:54.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  那个
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.43,0:17:00.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  礼弥同学偏凉性的吗  手像冰一样冷啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.71,0:17:02.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我  那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.62,0:17:07.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过没关系  马上就带你到超HOT的地方去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.79,0:17:09.79,Note2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有动作了啊{\i1}! {\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.29,0:17:12.79,Note2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道是察觉到我们的行动了吗{\i1}! {\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.79,0:17:14.54,Note2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能…  那他是哪路神仙?{\i1}!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.79,0:17:15.50,Note2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鬼知道{\i1}! {\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.78,0:17:17.84,Note2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不说这个  快追上去{\i1}! {\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.41,0:17:26.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  要到哪里去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.24,0:17:29.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶  要到外面去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.35,0:17:36.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有错  在亮丽的阳光中  让我们共享悠闲的二人时光吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.85,0:17:38.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.87,0:17:41.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  正好长凳空着呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.79,0:17:43.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那  那个
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.85,0:17:48.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我白天不太好在外面…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.16,0:17:50.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是  不行不行啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.00,0:17:53.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能一直待在有空调的地方啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.41,0:17:56.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看啊  这里风景很不错的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.41,0:17:58.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白净的礼弥同学虽然也很美丽
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.46,0:18:00.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是可不能不健康啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.13,0:18:05.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然那个男的还在  但是现在是好机会
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.55,0:18:07.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正好出口就在边上
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.44,0:18:10.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办  要上吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.94,0:18:10.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs20}来啊  阳光晒在身上好舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.81,0:18:12.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快快  快来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.54,0:18:14.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  上吧  执行
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.22,0:18:16.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个男的交给我了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.25,0:18:18.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,配合好时机
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.72,0:18:20.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,3
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.96,0:18:21.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,2
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.99,0:18:22.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,1
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.42,0:18:24.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Go
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.11,0:18:31.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.53,0:18:34.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,礼弥呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.83,0:19:05.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊  这股蛮力
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.86,0:19:09.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs20}啊…讨厌  降谷君
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.53,0:19:08.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大脑的限制真的解除了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.97,0:19:11.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讨厌
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.70,0:19:12.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,制不住她
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.85,0:19:16.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  跑哪去了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.50,0:19:20.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊啊啊  救命
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.89,0:19:21.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,礼弥
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.95,0:19:26.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,礼弥  怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.30,0:19:30.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讨厌  不要过来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.35,0:19:36.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…个  礼弥
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.40,0:19:44.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你来救我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.95,0:19:47.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  我什么都没做
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.36,0:19:50.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该说  长凳被…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.58,0:19:55.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肌肉还是跟原来一样  手臂会脱臼的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.40,0:20:00.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可怕啊  那些人想要绑架我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.15,0:20:03.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.05,0:20:08.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说回来  他们是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.13,0:20:10.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.35,0:20:12.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有  为什么康孝也在
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.38,0:20:15.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没  没有办法
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.69,0:20:17.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的话就改变计划
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.80,0:20:22.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  大叔你们是什么人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.47,0:20:24.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么要对礼弥出手
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.73,0:20:25.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,报警了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.27,0:20:28.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说话啊  干嘛保持沉默
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.65,0:20:31.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道说是散华家的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.35,0:20:34.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,后面
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.29,0:20:40.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等下  啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.58,0:20:49.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,散华  同学
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.60,0:20:50.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.44,0:21:09.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,降谷君！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.19,0:21:15.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.58,0:21:21.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本来打算执行计划抓住礼弥大人的  那个
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.81,0:21:16.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs20}可恶  
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.38,0:21:19.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs20}混蛋  放开我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.43,0:21:21.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs20}是谁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.93,0:21:25.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被难以置信的蛮力干扰  没能控制住
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.54,0:21:28.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不得已执行B计划了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.71,0:21:29.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…
